CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1945, pg. 2, reads: "From New England - Clarence Ried and his two daughters, Ruth, left, and Laura Jane, were recent guests of Mr. and Mrs. Forest Townes, of Burrows Street.  The Reids are residents of Boston, Mass. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Sisters Ruth and Laura Jane Reid posed in front of light colored background, Harris Studio
